These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: go, poker
City: colone, liverpool
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Game   | go  | poker |
| City     | liverpool | colone  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
House: ranch-style, modern
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch
1. the modern house is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| House    | ranch-style      | modern         |
| Nationality   | pakistani | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, gospel
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, van
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | pop   |
| Transport       | van  | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, purple
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Birthday   | march  | february |
| Color         | lilac | purple    |

 #################################

 
